videos.description: Kentavious Caldwell-Pope gets the inbound pass and pulls up to drain a drifting 3-point shot to beat the buzzer as the Lakers establish a 63-57 lead over the Bucks.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KCP splashes drifting 3-point shot to beat halftime buzzer) 2021/01/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: KCP splashes drifting 3-point shot to beat halftime buzzer

videos.description: Anthony Davis sets up LeBron James nicely with a bounce pass to lead him to the basket for an explosive two-handed finish at the rim.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD finds LeBron for powerful two-handed slam) 2021/01/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD finds LeBron for powerful two-handed slam

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo misses the 3-pointer but gets his own rebound and charges to the basket to stuff down a one-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis rebounds his own miss for big 2nd-chance slam) 2021/01/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis rebounds his own miss for big 2nd-chance slam

videos.description: Khris Middleton throws a pass through LeBron James's legs to Jrue Holiday in transition for the easy reverse layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Middleton nutmegs LeBron for a Bucks bucket) 2021/01/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Middleton nutmegs LeBron for a Bucks bucket

videos.description: LeBron James pulls up from 3 with a defender in his face and holds up three fingers before the shot goes in.
videos.headline: LeBron calls his 3-point shot

videos.description: LeBron James puts up his first 30-point game of the season as the Lakers take down Giannis Antetokounmpo and the Bucks 113-106.
